<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM7.5.4">
<l>veḷḷat tuḷḷō rālilaimēl mēvi yaṭiyēṉ maṉampukunteṉ</l>
<l>uḷḷat tuḷḷuṅ kaṇṇuḷḷum niṉṟār niṉṟa vūrpōlum</l>
<l>puḷḷup piḷḷaik kiraitēṭip pōṉa kātal peṭaiyōṭum</l>
<l>aḷḷal ceṟuvil kayalnāṭu maṇiyār vayalcū ḻaḻuntūrē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The city where stands the one who stays in [my] eyes and in my heart,</l>
<l>Having entered the mind of [this] servant, me,</l>
<l rend="indent">[and] having dwelled in a flood on a banyan leaf,</l>
<l>It seems is Aḻuntūr surrounded by beautiful paddy fields </l>
<l rend="indent">where a bird with its beloved mate,</l>
<l>Which went seeking food for [their] chicks, hunts kayal [fish]</l>
<l rend="indent">in the muddy fields.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
